        "message": "release: v2.1.3 — macOS support (Apple Silicon)\n\n- CI: matrix build (Windows + macOS aarch64), latest.json dual-platform\n- tauri.conf.json: add macOS bundle config (min macOS 11.0)\n- lib.rs: conditional compilation for cleanup_update_bak\n- tiff-convert.ts: detect ImageMagick on macOS, skip watermark + notify user\n- TitleBar: macOS window controls on left side (platform-aware)\n- Updater: latest.json includes darwin-aarch64 (.app.tar.gz) entry",
